title: Classic Rock: Bubblegum, Garage and Pop Nuggets (VA ) [Time Life
description:
Classic Rock: Bubblegum, Garage and Pop Nuggets (VA ) [Time Life Classic Rock Series Nr 29]
CD (1991) To Mp3 VBR 126-212 mbit/s
Included: Front Cover and this Info

Classic Rock: Bubblegum, Garage and Pop Nuggets features 22 original hits from the mid-'60s. Among the highlights are the Mojo Men's "Sit Down, I Think I Love You," the Sunrays' "I Live for the Sun," the Merry-Go-Round's "Live," the Lovin' Spoonful's "Rain on the Roof," the Knickerbockers' "One Track Mind," and Sunshine Company's "Back on the Street Again." Time-Life released several other volumes in the Classic Rock series that are of equally high quality.
